frames.caption: A regal figure stands atop a rocky, fiery landscape, wielding a staff with a glowing orb. A massive, serpentine dragon coils behind her, its eyes and mouth ablaze with fire. The scene is dramatic and filled with an aura of power and mysticism.
frames.description: The scene is set in a fantastical, apocalyptic landscape with a powerful, mythical atmosphere. The central figure, a queen or sorceress, commands attention with her elaborate attire and commanding presence. The dragon adds an element of danger and awe, enhancing the epic nature of the setting.

frames.caption: A regal woman stands confidently on a rocky outcrop, holding a staff with a fiery tip. Behind her, a majestic dragon with glowing eyes coils dramatically against a stormy sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting where a powerful woman and a dragon are central figures. The atmosphere is intense and mystical, with a backdrop of dark clouds and flames.
